<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 03:25:59 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>英伟达的预测抑制风险偏好，亚洲股市走低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-11-21/</link><description>亚洲股市周四下跌，此前人工智能宠儿英伟达(Nvidia)因营收预期低迷而令投资者失望，而美元走强，比特币因美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普(Donald Trump)提出的政策预期而创下历史新高。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 03:03:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>早间竞价：英伟达击败，但未能提供火花</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-11-20/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 21:48:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-11-20/</guid></item><item><title>中国国防部长拒绝与五角大楼负责人会面</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-defense-minister-declines-meeting-with-pentagon-chief-2024-11-20/</link><description>中国国防部长在老挝举行的国防领导人会议期间拒绝与美国国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀会面，五角大楼负责人周三表示，此举是不幸的。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 18:32:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-defense-minister-declines-meeting-with-pentagon-chief-2024-11-20/</guid></item><item><title>法国马克龙敦促习近平取消对中国干邑白兰地的关税，轩尼诗工人罢工</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/hennessy-workers-strike-frances-macron-urges-xi-drop-china-cognac-tariffs-2024-11-20/</link><description>在法国总统马克龙敦促中国国家主席习近平取消关税后，轩尼诗员工周三延长罢工，抗议轩尼诗计划在中国装瓶干邑以规避进口关税。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 16:43:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/hennessy-workers-strike-frances-macron-urges-xi-drop-china-cognac-tariffs-2024-11-20/</guid></item><item><title>首席执行官表示，意法半导体与华虹合作是因为芯片制造商需要中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/stmicro-partners-with-hua-hong-chipmakers-need-china-says-ceo-2024-11-20/</link><description>欧洲计算机芯片制造商意法半导体首席执行官周三宣布了与中国晶圆代工厂华虹合作的新计划，他认为在中国进行本地制造对其竞争地位至关重要。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 16:33:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/stmicro-partners-with-hua-hong-chipmakers-need-china-says-ceo-2024-11-20/</guid></item><item><title>中国生物科技公司来凯医药与礼来公司合作开发保肌减肥药物</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/china-based-biotech-laekna-teams-up-with-lilly-develop-muscle-preserving-obesity-2024-11-20/</link><description>生物技术公司周三表示，礼来公司和香港上市公司来凯医药将合作开发一种实验性肥胖药物，旨在帮助患者减肥同时保留肌肉。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 15:11:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/china-based-biotech-laekna-teams-up-with-lilly-develop-muscle-preserving-obesity-2024-11-20/</guid></item><item><title>国际原子能机构格罗西希望伊朗限制高浓缩铀库存</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/iaeas-grossi-hopes-irans-capping-highly-enriched-uranium-stock-holds-2024-11-20/</link><description>联合国核监察机构负责人拉斐尔·格罗西周三表示，他希望伊朗将铀库存限制在略低于武器级的水平的举措能够持续下去，因为该机构的董事会将通过一项西方起草的决议，该决议可能会破坏这一计划。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 14:01:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/iaeas-grossi-hopes-irans-capping-highly-enriched-uranium-stock-holds-2024-11-20/</guid></item><item><title>福特将在欧洲裁员以应对电动汽车转型，中国竞争对手遭受损失</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/ford-cut-14-european-jobs-blaming-ev-shift-rising-competition-2024-11-20/</link><description>福特周三表示，将裁员约 14% 的欧洲员工，并将近年来的亏损归咎于电动汽车需求疲软、政府对电动汽车转型的支持不力以及来自受补贴的中国竞争对手的竞争。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 13:32:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/ford-cut-14-european-jobs-blaming-ev-shift-rising-competition-2024-11-20/</guid></item><item><title>由于担心特朗普可能征收关税，券商认为 2025 年“不确定”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/brokerages-see-uncertain-2025-worries-over-potential-trump-tariffs-2024-11-20/</link><description>各大券商表示，美国政策的不确定性可能会在 2025 年小幅放缓全球经济增长。他们预计，美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普提议的关税将加剧全球市场的波动，引发通胀压力，进而限制主要央行放松货币政策的范围。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 13:02:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/brokerages-see-uncertain-2025-worries-over-potential-trump-tariffs-2024-11-20/</guid></item><item><title>中国小马智行寻求在美国大规模IPO中获得高达45.5亿美元的估值</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-robotaxi-firm-pony-ai-seeks-raise-up-260-mln-upsized-us-ipo-2024-11-20/</link><description>小马智行周三表示，其美国首次公开募股的目标估值高达 45.5 亿美元，这表明对这家中国机器人出租车公司期待已久的纽约上市的强劲需求。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 12:27:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-robotaxi-firm-pony-ai-seeks-raise-up-260-mln-upsized-us-ipo-2024-11-20/</guid></item><item><title>普京的间谍头子警告西方不要与俄罗斯发生直接军事冲突</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/putins-spy-chief-warns-west-against-direct-military-conflict-with-russia-2024-11-20/</link><description>俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京(Vladimir Putin)的间谍负责人周三警告西方，如果美国及其欧洲盟友因乌克兰问题与俄罗斯发生直接军事对抗，将面临灾难性后果的风险。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 12:02:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/putins-spy-chief-warns-west-against-direct-military-conflict-with-russia-2024-11-20/</guid></item><item><title>报告显示，中国带着援助和影响力重返太平洋</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-returns-pacific-with-aid-influence-push-report-shows-2024-11-20/</link><description>洛伊研究所关于对该地区援助的一份报告发现，中国已取代美国重新成为太平洋岛屿第二大双边捐助国，并通过支出来赢得影响力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 11:35:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-returns-pacific-with-aid-influence-push-report-shows-2024-11-20/</guid></item><item><title>丹麦军方表示，在数据电缆泄露后，他们正在与中国船只保持密切联系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/kremlin-says-absurd-suggest-russia-involved-baltic-sea-cable-damage-2024-11-20/</link><description>丹麦军方周三表示，在波罗的海的两根光纤数据通信电缆被切断几天后，它正在靠近一艘目前在丹麦水域闲置的中国船只。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 11:30:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/kremlin-says-absurd-suggest-russia-involved-baltic-sea-cable-damage-2024-11-20/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：英伟达守夜看到风险战胜安全</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-11-20/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 11:26:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-11-20/</guid></item><item><title>11月份亚洲从印度的航空燃油进口量创多年新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/asias-jet-fuel-imports-india-hit-multi-year-highs-november-2024-11-20/</link><description>行业消息人士和船舶追踪数据显示，由于炼油厂停运和中国出口减少抑制了供应，亚洲从印度进口的航空燃油将于 11 月达到多年高位，赶在冬季需求高峰之前。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 11:13:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/asias-jet-fuel-imports-india-hit-multi-year-highs-november-2024-11-20/</guid></item></channel></rss>